## Zotero Local API

Direct access to the Zotero library via CLI (requires Zotero desktop running with MCP plugin).

**Usage:** `r2 zotero <command>` (or `python .claude/scripts/zotero_cli.py <command>`)

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `ping` | Health check |
| `search [QUERY]` | Search library |
| `get-item KEY` | Get item by key |
| `find-item --doi DOI` | Find by identifier |
| `collections` | List all collections |
| `pdf-content ITEM_KEY` | Extract PDF text |
| `search-annotations [QUERY]` | Search annotations |
